history.content: Submit CS major application, let a CS adviser sign on the double major form, and submit the double major form with both signatures to 206 Evans.

Nearly a month ago I received approvals for declaring both Statistics and CS major. Since I applied to the Stat department first, I have my double major application form (I don't remember the exact name) and stat signature on it. Now, what should I do to officially declare the double major so that I can see both majors on Calcentral (now there's only Stat)?
